{"tid":2194710,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多對因為去留問題而散？","createTime":"2020-09-08T16:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T12:18:21.000Z","uid":70301,"like":71,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c02314e8c9bc13d00fe1259101e4bf1a761b03","tid":2194710,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T16:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想走，因為覺得香港冇前途冇希望冇得救<br />\n唔想將來嘅仔女共享支那人嘅榮耀，生生世世做支那人，唔想下半世要入集中營，想去外國重過新生活，呼吸自由嘅空氣<br />\n<br />\n佢就覺得我好似末日撚，被害妄想症咁，香港冇我想像中咁差，又想留低陪屋企人，再加上我同佢嘅工作都穩定，人工都尚算OK，所以佢想留喺香港買樓結婚，生兒育女。<br />\n<br />\n上星期我講咗一句：我絕對唔會喺香港生小朋友，佢聽完之後即刻好灰，話要冷靜下先<br />\n尋日就send 個msg過嚟話同我價值觀想法太大差異，冇可能繼續落去，喺屋企喊咗幾日，決定同我分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實冇乜嘢，我只係想上嚟圍個爐，取個暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f9700da01ea26adf281968b51144144183d964","tid":2194710,"uid":70301,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"五年情，就咁話散就散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而我準備好佢份生日禮物，而家重喺我間房度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8ae26a98f99849f15c3bfa007462f0f2ccd022","tid":2194710,"uid":63496,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a3c02314e8c9bc13d00fe1259101e4bf1a761b03","tid":2194710,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T16:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj